      <p>
        <strong>Coming in Day 2:</strong> We explore
        <strong>test-time compute scaling</strong>: using prompting
        strategies like chain-of-thought reasoning to extract more capability
        at inference. This represents a fundamental shift: instead of only
        scaling <em>training</em>, we can also scale <em>thinking</em>.
      </p>
    </div>

