      </svg>
      <p>
        <strong>Social Science Application.</strong>
        <a href="https://www.pnas.org/doi/10.1073/pnas.2314021121" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Bail (2024)</a>
        offers in <em>PNAS</em> a balanced assessment of integrating LLMs
        into social science workflows. He emphasises valid measurement,
        reproducibility, and the distinction between tasks where LLMs
        augment human researchers and tasks where they might introduce
        systematic error. A good frame for everything in this course.
      </p>
